    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>* This project was created as part of the graduation work at ChungKang College of Cultural Industries</strong></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Prove your abilities to the stars and become the brightest constellation!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In a world of countless tiers, stars are divided into zones based on the strength of their light.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The protagonist, Pio, born with a faint light, begins their journey in the lowest tier, the Graveyard of Stars, yet carries a deep longing for the upper tiers.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >To realize this dream, Pio takes on the <strong>Trials of the Stars</strong>, aiming to ascend to the higher realms.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3334400/extras/e8d8bf9e2124ba0e869fedb9dc02893e.avif?t=1740816514\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3334400/extras_big/e8d8bf9e2124ba0e869fedb9dc02893e.avif?t=1740816514 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Game Overview</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Pio is a unique action platformer where players use the terrain they stand on to attack enemies.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game's standout feature is that the player's bullets also serve as terrain.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3334400/extras/d10393add88d2150e883f553882ee72a.avif?t=1740816514\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3334400/extras_big/d10393add88d2150e883f553882ee72a.avif?t=1740816514 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The more bullets you fire, the smaller the terrain becomes, demanding precise control. On the other hand, conserving bullets means enduring the onslaught of powerful monsters.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Experience this innovative action gameplay as you strategically manage your terrain and bullets to overcome challenges!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Dreamlike Constellation Worldview</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As you continue to face challenges, a more dreamlike world of stars unfolds.<br>Embark on a shining journey and explore a unique world!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>'The Examination Hall of Stars'</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3334400/extras/16afb8bda48dade38c62083b1c6e0174.avif?t=1740816514\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3334400/extras_big/16afb8bda48dade38c62083b1c6e0174.avif?t=1740816514 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong> 'The Tomb of Stars'</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3334400/extras/c8e79b24fc701e4d7d52ec3f5f63a2c0.avif?t=1740816514\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3334400/extras_big/c8e79b24fc701e4d7d52ec3f5f63a2c0.avif?t=1740816514 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>'The City of Scattered Stars'</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3334400/extras/95af3e1974882fab35c3abbb0ce3625c.avif?t=1740816514\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3334400/extras_big/95af3e1974882fab35c3abbb0ce3625c.avif?t=1740816514 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>'Gort's Altar'</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3334400/extras/2e6df5a570007cc934bf08c7e207bf68.avif?t=1740816514\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3334400/extras_big/2e6df5a570007cc934bf08c7e207bf68.avif?t=1740816514 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
